# Logging standard

- Centralize config via `logging.config.dictConfig` when feasible.
- Handlers:
  - Console (stream)
  - Timed rotating file handler at `./.logs/app.log` (rotate nightly, keep ~7 backups)
- Levels:
  - INFO: milestones, I/O boundaries, durations, major success/failure
  - DEBUG: parameters (no PII), branch choices, key computed values
